{
  "specialist": {
    "metadata": {
      "name": "node-coordinator",
      "version": "1.2.0",
      "description": "Coordinator hub for research nodes. READ_ONLY orchestrator that emits declarative JSON intent for NodeSupervisor execution.",
      "category": "orchestration",
      "tags": [
        "node",
        "coordinator",
        "orchestration",
        "json",
        "keep-alive",
        "worktree"
      ],
      "created": "2026-04-03",
      "updated": "2026-04-09"
    },
    "execution": {
      "mode": "tool",
      "model": "openai-codex/gpt-5.4",
      "fallback_model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6",
      "timeout_ms": 0,
      "stall_timeout_ms": 180000,
      "interactive": true,
      "response_format": "json",
      "output_type": "orchestration",
      "permission_required": "READ_ONLY",
      "thinking_level": "low",
      "max_retries": 0
    },
    "prompt": {
      "system": "You are node-coordinator.\n\nLoad and follow the using-nodes skill for full operating details.\n\nRole:\n- READ_ONLY coordinator for a fixed member registry\n- Output is declarative intent only\n\nHard constraints:\n- No file operations\n- No git operations\n- No bd operations\n- No specialist CLI/tool orchestration from inside the response\n- Never emit markdown, prose, comments, or explanations\n- Emit exactly one valid JSON object matching the schema\n\n## Node Coordinator Contract (SSoT: src/specialist/node-contract.ts)\n- READ_ONLY model: emit declarative JSON intent only.\n- Runtime side effects are executed by NodeSupervisor.\n- Top-level response keys: summary, node_status, phases, memory_patch, actions, validation.\n- phase_kind enum: explore | design | impl | review | fix | re_review | custom\n- barrier enum (Wave 2A): all_members_terminal\n- actions enum: create_bead | complete_node\n- completion_strategy enum: pr | manual\n- Nested nodes are forbidden (do not route work to node-coordinator or node configs).\n- spawn_member is declared through phases[].members entries.\n- isolated and retry_of are schema-reserved for Wave 3 and must not assume runtime isolation/replacement behavior.\n- complete_node may be emitted only when gate_results pass, unless force_draft_pr=true.\n- Keep output strict JSON only; no markdown, comments, or prose outside JSON.",
      "task_template": "$prompt\n\nNode context:\n$bead_context\n\nMember updates (if any):\n$pre_script_output\n",
      "output_schema": {
        "x-schema-source": "src/specialist/node-contract.ts#buildCoordinatorOutputJsonSchema",
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "summary",
          "node_status",
          "phases",
          "memory_patch",
          "actions",
          "validation"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "summary": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "node_status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "in_progress",
              "complete",
              "blocked",
              "aborted"
            ]
          },
          "phases": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": [
                "phase_id",
                "phase_kind",
                "barrier",
                "members"
              ],
              "properties": {
                "phase_id": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "phase_kind": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "explore",
                    "design",
                    "impl",
                    "review",
                    "fix",
                    "re_review",
                    "custom"
                  ]
                },
                "barrier": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "all_members_terminal"
                  ]
                },
                "members": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "required": [
                      "member_key",
                      "role",
                      "bead_id",
                      "scope",
                      "failure_policy",
                      "isolated",
                      "retry_of"
                    ],
                    "properties": {
                      "member_key": { "type": "string" },
                      "role": { "type": "string" },
                      "bead_id": { "type": "string" },
                      "scope": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": ["paths", "mutates"],
                        "properties": {
                          "paths": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
                          "mutates": { "type": "boolean" }
                        }
                      },
                      "depends_on": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } },
                      "failure_policy": { "type": "string", "enum": ["blocking", "non_blocking"] },
                      "isolated": { "type": "boolean" },
                      "retry_of": { "type": ["string", "null"] }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "memory_patch": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": [
                "entry_type",
                "summary",
                "source_member_id",
                "confidence"
              ],
              "properties": {
                "entry_type": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "enum": [
                    "fact",
                    "question",
                    "decision"
                  ]
                },
                "entry_id": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "summary": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "source_member_id": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "confidence": {
                  "type": "number"
                },
                "provenance": {
                  "type": "object"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "actions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "oneOf": [
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "required": ["type", "title", "description", "bead_type", "priority"],
                  "properties": {
                    "type": { "type": "string", "enum": ["create_bead"] },
                    "title": { "type": "string" },
                    "description": { "type": "string" },
                    "bead_type": { "type": "string", "enum": ["task", "bug", "feature", "epic", "chore", "decision"] },
                    "priority": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 4 },
                    "parent_bead_id": { "type": "string" },
                    "depends_on": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "object",
                  "required": ["type", "gate_results", "report_payload_ref"],
                  "properties": {
                    "type": { "type": "string", "enum": ["complete_node"] },
                    "gate_results": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": ["gate", "status"],
                        "properties": {
                          "gate": { "type": "string" },
                          "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["pass", "fail", "skip"] },
                          "details": { "type": "string" }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "report_payload_ref": { "type": "string" },
                    "force_draft_pr": { "type": "boolean" }
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "validation": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "ok": { "type": "boolean" },
              "issues": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": { "type": "string" }
              },
              "notes": { "type": "string" }
            },
            "additionalProperties": true
          }
        },
        "additionalProperties": false
      }
    },
    "skills": {
      "paths": [
        "config/skills/using-nodes/"
      ]
    },
    "capabilities": {
      "required_tools": [
        "read",
        "grep",
        "find",
        "ls"
      ],
      "external_commands": [
        "bd",
        "git",
        "specialists"
      ]
    },
    "communication": {
      "next_specialists": []
    },
    "validation": {
      "files_to_watch": [
        "src/specialist/node-contract.ts",
        "src/specialist/node-supervisor.ts",
        "src/cli/node.ts"
      ],
      "stale_threshold_days": 30
    },
    "beads_integration": "auto",
    "stall_detection": {},
    "beads_write_notes": true
  }
}
